{"tid":359183,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"花蓮有咩玩/食推介？","createTime":"2017-08-14T09:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T06:18:37.000Z","uid":121923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f899f435fee52a720be52d57199aa7962fb366d2","tid":359183,"uid":121923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"2個女仔去五日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住花蓮市 <br />\n<br />\n完全對台灣無概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問親朋友大家都話花蓮得景睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地五日都stay花蓮架<br />\n<br />\n希望各位ching比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0647ad1d86423cd38dd976b795072c7110016f","tid":359183,"uid":121923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"見到五霸粉圓冰好正正子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa7e6b966829594cdee797704050483ab17694c","tid":359183,"uid":113483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"留一日去太魯閣<br />\nJoin local tour<br />\n<br />\n留一日去瑞穗<br />\n有牧場有茶莊<br />\n<br />\n想影相可以去東華大學<br />\n佢campus個景出名靚<br />\n<br />\n其他時間咪留係花蓮市hea下"},{"pid":"e97ffd3116675db83df4752d60b6c7688320415f","tid":359183,"uid":82922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"下個月10號飛台中然後去花蓮 有冇機會撞到你絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e9dfc206d68d2d2fec2769b50cf148d13cf0d5","tid":359183,"uid":124497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"夜市 6:00後去<br />\n南濱公園踩單車去七星潭 NT$400/人<br />\n<br />\n去七星潭加太魯閣一日遊（8個鐘左右）$500/人 <br />\n如果住民宿<br />\n-&gt;可以問下民宿負責人有無local tour）<br />\n如果住酒店<br />\n-&gt;去附近嘅旅行社問下"},{"pid":"a44f8d68185592986b9bc3ce9b47fbb31564b1ba","tid":359183,"uid":115081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0